## Academic Context

This project was developed by Paluku B as part of academic work in embedded 
systems and IoT. The code is freely available for educational, research, 
and commercial purposes.

## Attribution

When using this project in academic work, please cite as:
Paluku B. (2025). OPENDOM - Embedded Home Automation System. 
GitHub: https://github.com/palukuba/opendom-esp32

The project demonstrates practical implementation of:
- ESP32 embedded programming with FreeRTOS
- Real-time sensor data validation and processing  
- Progressive Web App (PWA) development
- IoT device integration and control
- Automated rule engine design
- Modern web interface design principles
